
@BASE_URL=http://localhost:3000

### cours active
GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/cours-started
Content-Type: application/json

### cours active avec id
GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/cours-started/1
Content-Type: application/json

### creer une cours active
POST {{BASE_URL}}/api/cours-started
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "userId": 1,
    "coursId": 2,
    "IsEnd": false
}



### modifier une cours active
PATCH {{BASE_URL}}/api/cours-started/4
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "userId": 1,
    "coursId": 3,
    "IsEnd": false
}

### supprimer une cours active
DELETE {{BASE_URL}}/api/cours-started/4
Content-Type: application/json
